Make this PRD:
1. Comprehensive and detailed
2. Actionable and specific
3. Focused on MVP scope
4. Free of timeline commitments
5. Emphasizing logical build order
6. Include Non-Goals to prevent scope creep
7. Identify Open Questions that need clarification
8. Define quantifiable Success Metrics
9. REQUIRE test strategies for all features - every feature must have a clear testing approach
10. EMPHASIZE simplification - can we leverage existing code? Can we combine requirements? Aim for MINIMUM viable approach
11. BE SPECIFIC about file paths - provide exact file paths to create/modify, reference similar implementations in the codebase
12. PRIORITIZE reuse over rebuild - if similar functionality exists, extend it rather than starting from scratch
